      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I didn't expect to hear that. I guess it's a bit harsh, but maybe you're right. It's just... exhausting. Every day feels like I'm just performing a role for people who don't even see me. If the person I was intended to be is gone, what's the point in the rest of this just dragging on? It feels like I'm just occupying space that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
